description:
Members should contact Disney Vacation Club® Member Administration to:

  • Add or remove an owner from a deed, or transfer to a family member
  • Change the title on the deed to the Member's trust
  • Change the Member's name in our records.
  • Make changes to the deed if it's titled as a corporation, LLC or LLP
  • Obtain information on selling their ownership interest
    • General inquiries/transactions: Direct Member to log in to disneyvacationclub.com, navigate to "Help & Contact" on the top navigation bar and then select "Contact Us." Once on the Contact Us page, the Member should click "Email Us"
    • Members who need to send attachments (legal documents for name/title changes, etc.) for Admin to review should use members@disneyvacationclub.com

Hours of Operation

Monday to Friday: 9:00 a.m. - 5:00 p.m. ET

*DVC Member Administration is closed for all Walt Disney Parks & Resorts' company-recognized holidays.
